<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Logout - Simulatore CFU UniMarconi</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(0deg, #379975 40px, #FFF 0%);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .logout-container {
            text-align: center;
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #E57552;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            color: #444444;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .info-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 2px solid #379975;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .btn {
            padding: 12px 24px;
            margin: 10px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #379975;
            color: white;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #2d7a5f;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="logout-container">
        <h1>Logout Completato</h1>
        <p>Sei stato disconnesso con successo dal sistema.</p>
        
        <div class="info-box">
            <h3 style="color: #379975; margin-top: 0;">ℹ️ Informazioni per l'accesso</h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                Per accedere nuovamente al sistema, è necessario un <strong>token valido</strong>.<br>
                Contatta l'amministratore per ottenere un nuovo token di accesso.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Torna alla Homepage</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
